    "id": "f_csv_f23ef47ca0",
    "slug": "lyn-this-was-the-aha-moment-when-desta-found-another-astonishing-skeleton-r",
    "texto": "Lyn, this was the “Aha!” moment when Desta found another astonishing skeleton. Remarkably, it appeared utterly human but existed before humans walked the Earth. Clutched in its hand a small sphere attached to an elaborate gold necklace. The sphere was not like any material on Earth. Remember when I told you our origins might lie in the stars? Well, I think we found the answer in the Afar desertMax",
